schema:description: "A complete Motor Hotel in a garden setting. The dining patio and pool are shown at the top right. The Chart Room for cocktails at bottom right. The Voyager Inn is located on Interstate 80, two miles east of the University of California Campus at Davis, and twelve miles west of the State Capitol at Sacramento. From the east take Mace Blvd. overpass and proceed one quarter miles to the west. From the west take Mace Blvd. exit on your right."
